@buildabearfoundation is proud to partner with @baby2baby to bring furry friends to the children and families they support.

Baby2Baby remains focused on providing children in need with backpacks, school supplies, and everything they need to start the school year off right. This allows parents who are still impacted by the pandemic to put their limited resources toward paying months of back rent, putting food on the table, and keeping their children safe.

To learn more about Build-A-Bear Foundation's partnerships, visit the link in their bio!
